<i>adverb</i>: 충실히 [충실히], 지성껏 [지성껃], 줄레줄레 [줄레줄레], 졸래졸래 [졸래졸래], 성실히 [성실히], 꾸벅꾸벅 [꾸벅꾸벅], 꼬박꼬박 [꼬박꼬박] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>충실히 [충실히]</dt><br>
<dd>faithfully; loyally; devotedly; truly</dd><br>
<dd>충성스럽고 정직하며 성실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a loyal, honest, and sincere manner.</dd><br>
<dt>지성껏 [지성껃]</dt><br>
<dd>faithfully; devotedly</dd><br>
<dd>온갖 정성을 다하여.</dd><br>
<dd>With all one's heart.</dd><br>
<dt>줄레줄레 [줄레줄레]</dt><br>
<dd>1. aimlessly</dd><br>
<dd>가볍고 조심성 없이 함부로 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting lightly and recklessly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. faithfully; in single file</dd><br>
<dd>남의 뒤를 무질서하게 자꾸 따라다니는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of continuously following someone or something in an uneven or somewhat disorderly fashion.</dd><br>
<dt>졸래졸래 [졸래졸래]</dt><br>
<dd>1. playfully</dd><br>
<dd>까불거리며 가볍게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of acting playfully and lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. faithfully; in single file</dd><br>
<dd>여럿이 질서가 없이 졸졸 뒤따르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of a group following someone or something in a disorderly fashion.</dd><br>
<dt>성실히 [성실히]</dt><br>
<dd>faithfully; sincerely</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 행동이 진실하고 정성스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Sincerely and genuinely in one's attitude or behavior.</dd><br>
<dt>꾸벅꾸벅 [꾸벅꾸벅]</dt><br>
<dd>faithfully</dd><br>
<dd>남이 시키는 대로 아무 말 없이 그대로 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of quietly doing something as one is told.</dd><br>
<dt>꼬박꼬박 [꼬박꼬박]</dt><br>
<dd>regularly; faithfully</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 한 번도 빠뜨리지 않고 계속하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of continuously doing something without skipping it even once.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>